### FAQ-032 | Category: Discounts&Points
Canonical Question: How many points can I earn each time I share the app? Is there a daily limit?
Keywords: many, points, earn, each, time, share, app, there, daily, limit, not, only
Answer:
You can earn points not only when your direct invitee joins or makes a purchase, but also from their referrals—up to three levels deep! Here’s how it works:
Example of the referral chain:
A invites B → A earns 2,500 points
B invites C → B earns 2,500 points, and A earns 1,500 points
C invites D → C earns 2,500 points, B earns 1,500 points, and A earns 1,000 points
D invites E → D earns 2,500 points, C earns 1,500 points, B earns 1,000 points (A receives nothing, as the reward stops at 3 levels)
Key rules:
Direct invite: 2,500 points per successful registration or first purchase
2nd level: 1,500 points
3rd level: 1,000 points
No rewards beyond the 3rd level
Earning limits:
Daily cap: Up to 50,000 points per user per day
Monthly cap: Up to 1,000,000 points per user per month
Once you reach either limit, no further points will be awarded until the quota resets at 00:00 the next day (daily) or 00:00 on the 1st of the following month (monthly).
Points are credited automatically once your referral completes the qualifying action.

