### FAQ-045 | Category: Orders
Canonical Question: How do l add my phone number and address to my account?
Keywords: add, phone, number, address, account, easily, update, contact, details, shipping, lulufulo, app
Answer:
You can easily update your contact details and shipping address in the LULUFULO app by following these steps:
To add or update your phone number:
1.Open the LULUFULO app and log in to your account.
2.Tap “Account” (bottom right corner) to go to your profile.
3.Go to “Settings” → “Profile”.
4.Find the “Phone NO.” field and tap the “Edit” button on the right.
5.Enter your phone number and complete the verification process as prompted.
