1.Open the LULUFULO app and log in to your account.
2.Tap “Account” → “Settings” → “Delivery Address”.
3.Tap “Add Address” at the bottom of the screen.
4.Fill in your full name, city, street address, phone number and any other required details.
5.Tap “Save” to confirm.
Make sure your contact and address information is accurate to avoid delays in order processing and delivery. If the problem persists, feel free to reach out to our customer support team—we’re here to help!

